name: Lilypad
description: Lilypad is a revolutionary serverless compute platform from Protocol Labs, democratizing high-performance computing. It operates by leveraging a network of GPU node operators, ensuring trust with optimistic reproducibility & on-chain guarantees. Lilypad sees compute as vital for an open web and AI, aiming to reach a broad user base. Developers can run internet-scale tasks from a smart contract, CLI, or SaaS, spanning AI, ML, gaming, DeFI & DeSci.
